---
layout: base.njk
title: You're In! | WealthBridge Consulting
description: Thank you for signing up for the free Keep Rate course. Check your email for your first lesson.
confirm_title: You're In!
confirm_subtitle: Check your inbox - your first lesson is on its way. Over the next 5 days, you'll learn the exact strategies the ultra-wealthy use to keep more of every dollar they earn.
confirm_steps:
  - text: Check your email - Your first lesson arrives within minutes
  - text: Add us to contacts - So lessons don't go to spam
  - text: Set aside 5 minutes daily - Each lesson is quick but powerful
confirm_cta_text: Ready to take the next step?
confirm_cta_button: Book Your Free Keep Rate Audit
---

<!-- Confirmation Section -->
<section class="confirmation section--cream">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="confirmation__card animate">
      <div class="confirmation__icon">
        <svg width="40" height="40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1 class="confirmation__title" data-editable="text" data-prop="confirm_title">{{ confirm_title }}</h1>

      <p class="confirmation__text" data-editable="text" data-prop="confirm_subtitle">{{ confirm_subtitle }}</p>

      <div class="confirmation__steps">
        <p class="confirmation__steps-title">What happens next:</p>
        <div class="confirmation__steps-list">
          {% for step in confirm_steps %}
          <div class="confirmation__step">
            <span class="confirmation__step-number">{{ loop.index }}</span>
            <span>{{ step.text | safe }}</span>
          </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top: 32px;">
        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: var(--slate); margin-bottom: 16px;" data-editable="text" data-prop="confirm_cta_text">{{ confirm_cta_text }}</p>
        <a href="/landing/book-audit/" class="btn btn--primary btn--large" data-editable="text" data-prop="confirm_cta_button">{{ confirm_cta_button }}</a>
        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 16px;">30 minutes. No obligation. Personalized insights.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
